            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x357a,
            "msg_string": "No, no, I just got here, too...<CR>Oh, who's this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x357b,
            "msg_string": "Oh, this is Juris. He's a huntsman and a master with a bow."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14e9,
            "msg_string": "And this is Regina. She's a prospector and is really knowledgeable about ruins."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x19e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14ea,
            "msg_string": "I'm Juris. Nice to meet you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x199,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14eb,
            "msg_string": "Well, well, nice to meet you, too...<CR>But still..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14ec,
            "msg_string": "Mm-hmm mm-hmm...th-this is...!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14ed,
            "msg_string": "I-Is something wrong...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14ee,
            "msg_string": "I don't mean to be rude all of a sudden, but you really resemble my brother..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14ef,
            "msg_string": "Your height and ambience...are totally alike."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14f0,
            "msg_string": "Your chest measurements are about the same, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x14f1,
            "msg_string": "Kyah! Regina, what are you doing!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x129,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x14f2,
            "msg_string": "Wha-What...are you doing!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14f3,
            "msg_string": "Don't move. I'm just gonna measure your chest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x12b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14f4,
            "msg_string": "No. Being Ayesha's guard has nothing to do with my chest measurements."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14f5,
            "msg_string": "Could you refrain from touching my body?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14f6,
            "msg_string": "Darn, what a shabby fella. You're definitely like my brother."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14f7,
            "msg_string": "Alright, I'll consider you to be my little brother from now on!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14f8,
            "msg_string": "Don't do that! I've never had an older sister."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14f9,
            "msg_string": "How boring..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14fa,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, I'm glad you two are getting along already."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14fb,
            "msg_string": "I'm happy. I'll be counting on you two from now on, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14fc,
            "msg_string": "How and why did you come to that conclusion after seeing what just happened...?"
        }
    ]
